    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Selfishness
---
The man who works for self, or thinksthat his business is being run for
hispersonal benefit, or who expects otherpeople to help him, can never
become asuccess. His very attitude toward lifekeeps away all possibilities
of such athing; it dams up the channel throughwhich good and abundance can
flow.
